{"article_id":"DS5BfTkv7EkaBEHV","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"WASHINGTON -","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"President Trump defended his administration 's response to the humanitarian disaster in Puerto Rico ,","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"dismissing any critics of his relief efforts as `` fake news '' and `` politically motivated ingrates . ''","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"`` We have done a great job with the almost impossible situation in Puerto Rico , ''","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"Trump said .","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"`` Outside of the Fake News or politically motivated ingrates ... people are now starting to recognize the amazing work","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"that has been done by FEMA and our great Military . ''","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"Trump 's comments follow a barrage of tweets on Saturday ,","depth":6},{"id":8,"text":"in which he directly targeted the mayor of San Juan , Carmen Yulin Cruz ,","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"who had questioned the pace or relief efforts to the island","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"battered by Hurricane Maria .","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"While Trump accused the mayor of acting as the behest of Democrats","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"`` to be nasty to Trump , ''","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"Cruz said","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"she was only appealing for quicker help","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"to save lives .","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"`` I was n't saying anything nasty about the president , ''","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"Cruz told MSNBC .","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"More :","depth":5},{"id":19,"text":"Trump blasts Puerto Rican mayor for 'poor leadership ' in hurricane relief crisis","depth":5},{"id":20,"text":"More :","depth":6},{"id":21,"text":"Trump resumes defense of Puerto Rico disaster response , with apparent attack on San Juan mayor","depth":6},{"id":22,"text":"More :","depth":7},{"id":23,"text":"Former CIA director obliquely questions Trump 's leadership in Puerto Rico crisis","depth":7},{"id":24,"text":"More :","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"By the numbers :","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"Hurricane Maria damage , recovery in Puerto Rico","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"Trump is scheduled to visit the island Tuesday","depth":7},{"id":28,"text":"to review rescue efforts .","depth":7},{"id":29,"text":"He may also visit the U.S. Virgin Islands ,","depth":7},{"id":30,"text":"which is also undergoing a hurricane relief effort .","depth":7},{"id":31,"text":"As Trump prepares for the trip ,","depth":6},{"id":32,"text":"Puerto Rico National Guard Maj. Paul Dahlen said","depth":7},{"id":33,"text":"the president ' s expected visit to the island is not affecting aid deliveries or any other relief operations .","depth":7},{"id":34,"text":"In a third tweet on Sunday morning , Trump had kind words for Puerto Rico Gov . Ricardo Rossello ,","depth":7},{"id":35,"text":"thanking him and `` all of those","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"who are working so closely with our First Responders .","depth":9},{"id":37,"text":"Fantastic job ! ''","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"Rossello told reporters Sunday","depth":8},{"id":39,"text":"that the U.S. Defense Department has increased its presence on the island ,","depth":9},{"id":40,"text":"and that the emphasis remains on ensuring that \" food , water and other the supplies get delivered to the people of Puerto Rico. \"","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"However ,","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"when asked whether all buildings were inspected for safety","depth":11},{"id":43,"text":"as Trump had claimed ,","depth":11},{"id":44,"text":"Rossello said :","depth":10},{"id":45,"text":"`` I ' m not sure about that .","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"There are areas in Puerto Rico","depth":10},{"id":47,"text":"that we haven ' t gotten in contact . ''","depth":10},{"id":48,"text":"Trump also drew fire on Saturday","depth":7},{"id":49,"text":"for saying","depth":8},{"id":50,"text":"some people in Puerto Rico `` want everything to be done for them","depth":9},{"id":51,"text":"when it should be a community effort .","depth":9},{"id":52,"text":"10,000 Federal workers now on Island","depth":7},{"id":53,"text":"doing a fantastic job . ''","depth":7},{"id":54,"text":"FEMA Administrator Brock Long said on Fox News Sunday","depth":7},{"id":55,"text":"that relief efforts on the island represent one of the most logistically challenging undertakings","depth":9},{"id":56,"text":"the country has ever faced ,","depth":9},{"id":57,"text":"particularly coming so soon on the heels of other hurricanes .","depth":8},{"id":58,"text":"He acknowledged","depth":8},{"id":59,"text":"major challenges remain","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"and there 's still a `` long way to go , ''","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"but he said","depth":10},{"id":62,"text":"a lot has been accomplished .","depth":10},{"id":63,"text":"`` What I do n't have patience for is the fact","depth":9},{"id":64,"text":"that what we 're trying to do","depth":12},{"id":65,"text":"and what we have successfully done","depth":12},{"id":66,"text":"is we 've established a joint field office in San Juan ...","depth":11},{"id":67,"text":"where we 're having daily conversations with all the mayors ,","depth":11},{"id":68,"text":"we 're working with the governor and his leadership","depth":12},{"id":69,"text":"to create unified objectives , ''","depth":12},{"id":70,"text":"Long said .","depth":8},{"id":71,"text":"Long also dismissed criticism of the federal relief efforts ,","depth":8},{"id":72,"text":"including from Cruz .","depth":8},{"id":73,"text":"`` We can choose to look at what the mayor spouts off or what other people spout off ,","depth":8},{"id":74,"text":"but we can also choose to see what 's actually being done ,","depth":9},{"id":75,"text":"and that ' s what I would ask . ''","depth":9},{"id":76,"text":"Treasury Secretary Steven Mnuchin said Sunday","depth":8},{"id":77,"text":"that the San Juan mayor 's complaints about the pace of aid were `` unfair ''","depth":9},{"id":78,"text":"given everything","depth":10},{"id":79,"text":"that 's been done .","depth":10},{"id":80,"text":"`` When the president gets attacked ,","depth":9},{"id":81,"text":"he attacks back , ''","depth":9},{"id":82,"text":"Mnuchin said on NBC 's Meet the Press .","depth":8},{"id":83,"text":"After getting generally high marks for his administration 's handling of hurricanes Harvey and Irma ,","depth":7},{"id":84,"text":"Trump has now found himself on the defensive for the preparations for Maria .","depth":7},{"id":85,"text":"Political opponents contrasted his approach to Puerto Rico to his recent hurricane recovery efforts in Texas and Florida ,","depth":8},{"id":86,"text":"for which the president spent the weekend at Camp David","depth":10},{"id":87,"text":"working on disaster response","depth":10},{"id":88,"text":"and tweeted ongoing messages of support for the damaged areas on the mainland .","depth":9},{"id":89,"text":"Sen. Bernie Sanders , I-Vt. ,","depth":12},{"id":90,"text":"speaking on CNN 's State of the Union ,","depth":12},{"id":91,"text":"suggested","depth":11},{"id":92,"text":"skin color may be a factor in Trump 's response .","depth":10},{"id":93,"text":"He also noted","depth":11},{"id":94,"text":"that Trump tweet-bombed the San Juan mayor from his `` fancy golf club '' in New Jersey ,","depth":13},{"id":95,"text":"where he is spending the weekend ,","depth":13},{"id":96,"text":"while mayor Cruz copes with a lack of food , water , and electricity .","depth":12},{"id":97,"text":"`` It is unspeakable , ''","depth":12},{"id":98,"text":"Sanders said .","depth":12},{"id":99,"text":"`` I do n't know","depth":12},{"id":100,"text":"what world Trump is living in . ''","depth":12},{"id":101,"text":"Ohio Republican Gov . John Kasich , also on CNN , said","depth":10},{"id":102,"text":"`` it 's not appropriate '' for Trump to criticize public officials","depth":11},{"id":103,"text":"who are `` in the middle of a disaster . ''","depth":11},{"id":104,"text":"Mick Mulvaney , Trump 's director of the Office of Management and Budget , said","depth":11},{"id":105,"text":"the president is saying","depth":12},{"id":106,"text":"that ,","depth":13},{"id":107,"text":"because of the island 's location ,","depth":14},{"id":108,"text":"the recovery project in Puerto Rico was always going to be tougher than the ones in Florida and Texas .","depth":14},{"id":109,"text":"`` This is an island","depth":13},{"id":110,"text":"that was absolutely devastated , ''","depth":13},{"id":111,"text":"Mulvaney said on CNN .","depth":12},{"id":112,"text":"`` This was always going to be harder . ''","depth":11},{"id":113,"text":"Cruz herself appeared to dismiss Trump 's tweets during an interview on ABC 's This Week ,","depth":7},{"id":114,"text":"saying","depth":8},{"id":115,"text":"that `` any dialogue","depth":10},{"id":116,"text":"that goes on","depth":10},{"id":117,"text":"just has to be able to produce results . ''","depth":9},{"id":118,"text":"As for Trump 's visit , Cruz said ,","depth":7},{"id":119,"text":"`` If he asks to meet with me ,","depth":8},{"id":120,"text":"of course I will meet with him . ''","depth":8}],"relations":[{"parent":241,"left":0,"right":240,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":240,"left":146,"right":239,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":146,"left":137,"right":145,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":137,"left":126,"right":136,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":126,"left":122,"right":125,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":122,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":125,"left":123,"right":124,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":123,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":124,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":136,"left":129,"right":135,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":129,"left":7,"right":128,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":128,"left"